      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Shaman&amp;message.id=5542#M5542</link>
      <description>Below level 50, skill caps for weapon skills is 5 + 5 per level, capped at 200.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;At level 50 and above, 1HB, 2HB and Piercing can be raised, but I'm not sure about intermediate caps.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;AT level 70, 1HB, 2HB and Piercing are capped at 215.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;We cannot raise our skill in 1HS/2HS (even though we can use some slashing weapons).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Also, H2H is capped at 75.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;We do not get any other ones (kick, bash, etc.); however, if you are a large race, you get racial bash/slam - capped at 1.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;I used bind wound a lot in the 20s and 30s. I don't know if it plays a part of today's game or not.</description>
